First Department,

February, 1945.

(February 2, 1945.) Louis Hinderstein, Respondent, v. Equitable Life Assurance Society of the United States, Appellant.

Determination unanimously affirmed, with costs and disbursements. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., Townley, Glennon, Cohn and Callahan, JJ.
